reviews.text: I work here and it is a great place to eat and shop. There is a hiking trail here so all good all-round

Tong Chong Street Market Beer Festival - Swire did a great job building a cool culture for Taikoo Place. A lot of new restaurants opening in the neighbourhood too. Also, there's an app (Taikoo Place) for all the cool things happening in the area, like pop-up stores and different discounts and events to join.
Very good signage with warm building care taker direction.
The area is neat...or tidy....when  night fall you will see the hidden beauty of this place....
We need more independent coffee shops in the complex, and especially in the buildings
